{"tid":1098549,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"求戲名！！","createTime":"2019-04-09T06:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T06:54:39.000Z","uid":135191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ea685386f81d997fcbbeb1b176ac94f2a0e8e5","tid":1098549,"uid":135191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:45:28.000Z","msg":"好耐以前睇過一套外國電影，好想睇返但完全唔記得個名叫咩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n套戲內容大概係咁（可能會有啲出入）：<br />\n係呢個世界入面嘅人每朝都要注射一種藥，好似係為咗斷咗啲人嘅七情六慾、記憶etc 有日男主角就好似鍾意咗個女仔（但正常黎講係冇可能），佢之後就反思點解要每日注射藥物但從來冇人同過佢地講點解，之後佢就停咗藥發現自己係有「情感」呢樣野。<br />\n<br />\n之後唔知點樣佢發現佢爹地嘅工作係殺死啲初生嬰兒，但政府同佢地講係送啲BB去好開心嘅地方，但其實係將佢地安樂死。<br />\n<br />\n男主角又唔知點樣識到一個有以前記憶同埋可以比人感受痛楚嘅老人家，男主角就日日搵佢傾計。個老人家係類似嘅繼承人咁，成個世界得佢一個知道咩係痛苦，係佢死之前就要搵到下個繼承佢...<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，可能有啲亂，我已經盡量記起啲情節<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望有人知係咩戲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3496a062b63d89fa2f5035050e5c2e8683d6597","tid":1098549,"uid":221596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:52:28.000Z","msg":"未來叛變?"},{"pid":"d9bf6c8631011379ed34d23bae26e8fe0487021f","tid":1098549,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:52:57.000Z","msg":"the giver"},{"pid":"25f2e584dcf7029919826f3f01ce5c0714ff6794","tid":1098549,"uid":135191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9bf6c8631011379ed34d23bae26e8fe0487021f","tid":1098549,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:52:57.000Z","msg":"the giver"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:53:51.000Z","msg":"Yes!!!!謝謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gi